- -11. 2. 2026 suspicion - 40% drop in laying rate and increase mortality in one hall
- -on-site inspection, official samples, preliminary veterinary measures
- -3 halls on the farm, as of February 11, 2026, the following numbers of animals were kept: H1 - 2,544 ducks, H2 - 2,348 ducks, H3 1,897 ducks.
